title: Bolivia Presidential Election
description:
General elections are scheduled to take place in Bolivia on 17 August 2025.

This market will resolve according to the listed candidate that wins this election. 

This market includes any potential second round. If the result of this election isn't known by December 31, 2025, 11:59 PM ET, the market will resolve to "Other".

This market will resolve based on the result of the election as indicated by a consensus of credible reporting. If there is ambiguity, this market will resolve based solely on the official results as reported by the Bolivian government, specifically the Plurinational Electoral Body (Órgano Electoral Plurinacional, OEP) (https://www.oep.org.bo/).

title: UFC 319: Du Plessis vs. Chimaev
description: This is a polymarket on the outcomes and results of the UFC 319: Du Plessis vs. Chimaev event.

markets.question: UFC 319: Du Plessis vs. Chimaev
markets.description:
This is a polymarket on whether Dricus Du Plessis or Khamzat Chimaev will win their bout at UFC 319, scheduled for August 16, 2025.

This market will resolve to "Du Plessis" if Dricus Du Plessis is declared the winner.
This market will resolve to "Chimaev" if Khamzat Chimaev is declared the winner.

If the fight is declared a draw, or if for any reason the bout is not scored, postponed after August 30, 2025, or canceled, this market will resolve 50–50.

The primary resolution source will be ESPN. A consensus of credible reporting may also be used.

markets.question: UFC 319: Murphy vs. Pico
markets.description:
This is a polymarket on whether Lerone Murphy or Aaron Pico will win their bout at UFC 319, scheduled for August 16, 2025.
